questions.scenario:
You are debugging a production issue where a service leaks memory. You identify a custom `Aspect` that tracks user sessions using `ThreadLocal`. Here is the code snippet:

java
@Aspect
@Component
public class SessionTrackerAspect {
    private static final ThreadLocal<UserSession> sessionStore = new ThreadLocal<>();

    @Around("@annotation(trackSession)")
    public Object monitor(ProceedingJoinPoint pjp, TrackSession trackSession) throws Throwable {
        sessionStore.set(new UserSession(SecurityContextHolder.getContext().getAuthentication()));
        try {
            return pjp.proceed();
        } finally {
            // Missing: sessionStore.remove();
        }
    }
}
